      "content": "That makes sense. I want to get a bit more specific on the grooming part. Specifically for hair—if we have diverse people in the room, what kind of hairstyles would you say best fit that 'polished' and 'authoritative' look you're talking about? I want to make sure everyone knows how to present themselves so there's no distraction during big pitches.",
